# GhosttyKit static libraries are large build artifacts (~800 MB), produced by
# scripts/refresh-ghostty.sh from the Ghostty fork. Kept OUT of git — they live
# on disk locally and are distributed as a GitHub Release asset. A fresh clone
# fetches/builds them before the first Xcode build.
Frameworks/GhosttyKit.xcframework/**/*.a
